review: The experience with the doctor was very good. Root Canal treatment was performed patiently by the doctor giving appropriate time for annesthesia to be effective and complete procedure to be painless. There is no pain even after root canal as proper medicines were prescribed by the doctor. Good job done by the doctor. I hope my repaired tooth will last for life long after this treatment.
